data.description: Motivated seller! Bring us your best offer!!! Looking for your own private oasis? Then look no further. This beautiful waterfront home boasts an open-space concept with 4 spacious bedrooms, and 3 full sized bathrooms. This home built in the late 1900s has been beautifully remodeled with some modern updates, however, it still has that country and southern charm to highlight this home's character. With over 2800 sqft, there's plenty of room for the family. Enjoy the waterfront view of the pond all from the comfort of the family room, or step outside onto the semi wrap around porch to enjoy the nice cool breeze. The kitchen has a nice wood stained wet bar and stainless steel appliances along with an additional island so there's plenty of room for the chef. New cork flooring, tile, light fixtures, updated bathrooms, new gas stove, new propane tank, new drywall, new painting, and so much more. This home is situated on 47.93 acres and has a beautiful pond, a chicken coop, a barn with electricity and a workshop, a green house, a garden, backyard storage, an open and will lit crawl space, Hvac system, solar panels, and 3 wells just to name a few. This income generating property has approximately 30 acres of cultivated land currently being leased. There's also plenty of land with sellable timber. Along with the home, comes an ATV, zero turn lawnmower, lawn equipment, garden and zone equipment. This property is under conservation use. Also with the home, comes some furniture as listed in the SD. There is so much more, but you need to see it to believe it. Schedule your appointment today. Client will review all offers, so submit your best before it's too late.
